# ── Data ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Synthetic data is regenerable from config/sim.yaml + a fixed seed
# (forecasting/docs/simulated_data), so it isn't committed. data/_truth/ is the
# hidden oracle (scoring only) and must never be version-controlled. We ignore the
# CONTENTS but keep each dir's .gitkeep so the skeleton is tracked on a fresh clone.
/data/raw/*
!/data/raw/.gitkeep
/data/interim/*
!/data/interim/.gitkeep
/data/processed/*
!/data/processed/.gitkeep
/data/_truth/*
!/data/_truth/.gitkeep
*.duckdb

# ── On-ramp app DB (W5) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# The designated application database (docs/website_production_overview.md §3) — SQLite by
# default, on-ramp-private, and deliberately NOT under /data/ above (that directory is the
# platform seam, owned by neither peer; the app DB never crosses it).
/onramp/plate_cost/instance/

# ── Models & experiment tracking ─────────────────────────────────────
# Regenerable and potentially large; the registry itself is Phase 8+ (rule 04).
/models/
mlruns/
mlartifacts/

# ── Python ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.ipynb_checkpoints/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/
*.egg-info/
build/
dist/

# ── Environments & secrets ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Phase 5 brings weather/events API keys — keep them out of git.
.venv/
venv/
env/
.env

# ── OS / editor ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# ── Claude Code — personal, machine-local permission grants ──────────
# settings.local.json accumulates broad "always allow" grants from interactive
# approvals; it isn't meant to be shared (docs/agentic_workflow/efficiency_backlog.md #5).
.claude/settings.local.json
